Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司 快躲开！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.87,0:01:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-剑司！\N-近藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.46,0:01:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍穹 - 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“痛楚”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异界体！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.07,0:02:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已经下定决心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.98,0:02:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.52,0:02:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异界体 我就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所教你的战斗方法的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是消耗战！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是要忍受痛楚的战法！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是战斗的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是存在的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.36,0:02:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是面对死亡的恐惧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异界体！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要留在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要留在这里啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的攻击出现停滞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.51,0:03:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军陆续突破防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进！别放过这个机会！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能不断前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要像是这样变成这座岛就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会拥抱住你们大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此我要和龙宫岛合而为一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回归吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们回归虚无吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.34,0:04:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快散开！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要感谢自己还活着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是存在于这里的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.73,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异界体…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…C地点…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见 使用缚狼刃索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.18,0:06:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是能让人类跟异界体共存的资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也太多了吧 会超载的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 大部分都正传送到别处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙宫岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北极传来资料了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔维斯的所有伺服器及兀尔德之泉已自动接收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是庞大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远超过之前接收的资料量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.43,0:06:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑他们已经抵达了红音的意志跟希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路线净空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系统正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.50,0:06:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导航系统正重新接收目标周边的相关情报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁红音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经告诉绝望的我们 要我们活下去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士…就在里面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敌人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会…让你们进去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始进行核心的再同步作业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过禁止通行了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们抢走的东西还给我们吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.32,0:08:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.83,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌方星核的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.99,0:09:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敌人的意识同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“接受”也是一种力量喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧 就在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.11,0:10:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…还在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑？你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.49,0:10:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为同化的关系 肉体的同化现象复发了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受治疗一定会康复的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到岛上吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核…开始行动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正前方出现敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的同化开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎么会这样…\N-乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人的星核正想和天空连系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它想要和大气层外的异界体一起覆盖住整个地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化Mark VII武器攻击它！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扳机由真矢来按
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将Mark Zein的能量用最大的功率释放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会只有一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多的话一骑的身体无法负荷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对它们来说 那或许是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也不是最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个星核也跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阐述生与死、存在与虚无是表里合一不断延续的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会诞生在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 你回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.05,0:13:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到另一个星核的身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.40,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异界体…全都往下掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沟口先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认法夫那部队所有驾驶员平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办到了 他们办到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地底…起风了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.36,0:14:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心和岛合而为一了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.95,0:14:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就可以回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.89,0:14:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Nicht！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核用自己的死亡赋予异界体成为了个体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.70,0:15:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去会拖累所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.73,0:15:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.90,0:15:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来 远见！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.88,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑！一骑！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.39,0:15:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来！同步直接连结还没中断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要少了任何一人 同步连结就没有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你在战斗之前告诉我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…他还活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在于任何地方 存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在与虚无正相互对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在于任何地方…存在于这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…总士…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是将一切回归虚无 来自异界体的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕在现实的世界中 我们的存在已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…还在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.85,0:16:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:45.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人类的宇宙舰队以及大气层外的异界体核心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方都燃烧殆尽而坠落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整艘舰艇在出发之前就被摧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是引擎仍然毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将机体的构造同化 把控制权交由系统管理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.59,0:17:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飞之后就由我来操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飞吗 一骑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然能飞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.36,0:17:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我陪着你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核理解生命的循环了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乙姬吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她本人是不可能再生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.45,0:18:15.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那将只是复制出同样的事物 违背了生命的本质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经是乙姬的存在转生成为新的事物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么她终将成长为核心 并且能够与我们对话的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.57,0:18:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们把这座岛当作希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且继续留在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.81,0:18:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续直走就能回到岛上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来还是你救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 我教导异界体什么是痛楚与存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.26,0:18:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也理解了他们的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解了存在与虚无的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在与虚无的循环？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经几乎不存在了 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到岛上一起接受治疗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一来一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么做吧 一骑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.62,0:19:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了 总士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会到异界体那里一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再度创造出自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道会花上多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 你在吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士…总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我们重逢为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VII的紧急修理完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.35,0:20:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以出动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员的精神状态也稳定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开第七巨龙之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark VII 出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.17,0:21:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.51,0:21:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在这里等你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:02.47,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂无知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.88,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}眺望着梦想的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:16.93,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,3000)\fs20\be1}再见了 湛蓝的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:35.34,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使将珍贵的事物当成跳板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:41.44,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}也想摘下最高处的苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:47.55,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}失去了才察觉到值得尊崇的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:54.96,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1800)\fs20\be1}年幼的我们总是不得要领
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:59.57,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}充盈于每一天的镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.76,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}使得情绪变得不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:08.84,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使受伤也祈祷能拍动羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:15.31,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂无知吧 眺望着梦想的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:21.29,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1000)\fs20\be1}再见了 湛蓝的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:33.48,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}正因为保持距离 才能得知自由的份量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:39.85,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}未成熟的心甚至无法理解这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:46.08,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}现在就敢如此断言吧 这里就是所谓的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:51.72,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1300)\fs20\be1}再见了 湛蓝的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:02.47,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}愚かでいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:06.88,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:16.93,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,3000)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:35.34,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}大切な何かを　踏み台にしてまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:41.44,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}一番高い林檎　掴みたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.55,0:21:47.55,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}無くしてから気付く　尊いモノ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:54.96,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1800)\an9\fs18\be1}幼い僕等は　的はずれだらけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.63,0:21:59.57,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}満ち足りた日々の制圧は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.76,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}情緒不安定になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:08.84,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}傷を負ってでも　羽ばたきたいと願うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:15.31,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}愚かでいいのだろう　見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.39,0:22:21.29,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.57,0:22:33.48,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}距離をおいてこそ　自分の大きさを知る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:39.85,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}未熟な心は　それさえ分からないまま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:46.08,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\an9\fs18\be1}今なら言えるだろう　此処がそう楽園さ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:51.72,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1300)\an9\fs18\be1}さよなら　蒼き日々よ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.63,0:22:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我就能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:23:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是充满痛苦的人生 我还是会选择存在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.11,0:23:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能够再度见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.85,0:23:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.28,0:23:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我一定会回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.65,0:23:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到有你在的地方…
